Usage: reset_min_pulse_width [-help] [<object_list>] [-high] [-low]
                             [-waveform_aware_type {absolute source_width_ratio all}]

-help             # Prints out the command usage
<object_list>     # List of objects: pins, ports or clocks (string, optional)
-high             # Specifies for high min pulse width (bool, optional)
-low              # Specifies for low min pulse width (bool, optional)
-waveform_aware_type {absolute source_width_ratio all}
                  # waveform aware pulse width check type to be reset (enum, optional)